129
00:15:04,038 --> 00:15:05,861
"The wind is rising.

130
00:15:05,881 --> 00:15:07,704
We must try to live."

131
00:16:01,085 --> 00:16:02,226
Earthquake.

132
00:16:54,138 --> 00:16:56,489
The boiler's going to blow!

133
00:17:06,493 --> 00:17:07,461
- What's wrong?

134
00:17:07,481 --> 00:17:08,449
- Her leg.

135
00:17:08,610 --> 00:17:09,794
Show me.

136
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:13,130
It hurts.

137
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:14,590
Kinu, be brave.

138
00:17:14,668 --> 00:17:16,011
It's broken.

139
00:17:16,031 --> 00:17:17,374
She can't walk like this.

140
00:17:17,588 --> 00:17:19,098
Miss, the boiler.

141
00:17:19,118 --> 00:17:20,628
Please save yourself.

142
00:17:20,664 --> 00:17:22,306
That's nonsense.

143
00:17:23,625 --> 00:17:25,977
Nothing's going to explode.

144
00:17:28,172 --> 00:17:29,480
My suitcase.

145
00:17:36,013 --> 00:17:38,197
Now, try to relax.

146
00:17:43,447 --> 00:17:44,707
She can't walk.

147
00:17:44,727 --> 00:17:45,987
Where do you live?

148
00:17:46,033 --> 00:17:47,334
- In Ueno.

149
00:17:47,354 --> 00:17:48,655
- I'll get you there.

150
00:18:01,298 --> 00:18:02,308
- Fire.

151
00:18:02,328 --> 00:18:03,338
- Let's go.

152
00:18:18,690 --> 00:18:20,055
- What about your luggage?

153
00:18:20,075 --> 00:18:21,440
- It's not important.

154
00:18:44,414 --> 00:18:46,390
I'm so sorry.

155
00:18:46,542 --> 00:18:47,892
Hang on!

156
00:18:58,095 --> 00:18:59,445
We'd better hurry.

157
00:19:43,609 --> 00:19:45,098
One of my shirts.

158
00:19:45,118 --> 00:19:46,607
It's brand new.

159
00:19:46,727 --> 00:19:48,285
You must be thirsty.

160
